- extends "base.haml"
- block title
  element43 - Random Market Scanner
- block content
  %h1
    Market Scanner
  .row
    .span5
      %h2{'style':'margin-bottom:0.4em;'}
        Speed
      %span#slider-label
        3 seconds per Item
      #slider
    .span6
      %h2
        Progress
      .progress
        #scan_progress.bar{'style':'width:0%;'}
  #speed-notice.alert.alert-info
    If your market window does not update anymore, reopen the IGB and pick a slower speed (3 seconds should be a good value).
  #scan_table_container
    %table#scan_table.table.table-condensed
      %tbody
        - for type in types
          %tr{'id':'{{type.id}}'}
            %td
              %img{'src':format('http://image.eveonline.com/type/{{type.id}}_32.png'), 'alt':'type image'}
            %td
              = type.name
- block scripts
  %script{'type':'text/javascript', 'src':'http://code.jquery.com/ui/1.8.22/jquery-ui.min.js'}
  %script{'type':'text/javascript', 'src':'/static/javascripts/jquery.pulse.js'}
  %script{'type':'text/javascript', 'src':'/static/javascripts/scanner.js'}